data.description:
Enjoy public lake access just 30 seconds from home. Three bedroom, 2 Full bath manufactured home on half acre lot. 
Metal outbuilding 8x10, 2 Metal carport 22x24 and 22x30. Gas rock fireplace in great room. Kitchen with marble island. Like new see through refrigerator. Smooth top oven, washer and dryer stays, LVP in bathroom and kitchen.
Covered outdoor dining area with smoker grill. Roof 2019 All landscape lighting is wired under ground. Whiskey kegs remain, swing, also double smoker grill ,Wood stove .
